data.description: This well maintained house is just minutes from town offering a country feel. The house has a split bedroom layout. Primary suite features a shower plus a soaker tub.  Living area has a fireplace plus large dining area overlooking the backyard. Step out into the Backyard overlooking a fenced in pasture and a 900sqft shop. The shop has ac with a 50 amp breaker and dual overhead doors. This one has it all dont miss out make a appointment today!!!
